---
import Button from '@/components/shared/Button.astro';
import classes from '@/data/styles.json';
---

<section class="bg-background-secondary py-24" id="about">
  <div class={classes.container}>
    <div class="flex flex-row gap-8">
      <div class="w-1/3">
        <h2 class={classes.heading}>
          Obsessed with <span class="text-gray-400">every detail.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class={classes.secondaryText}>
          I believe that the difference between good and great lies in the nuances. From the
          fluidity of an animation to the semantic structure of the DOM, I pour attention into every
          aspect of the frontend experience.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-4">
          <Button style="tertiary" href="#about-detail"> More about my process </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid w-2/3 grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div
          class="border-border-tertiary bg-card-primary transform rounded-3xl border p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          <span class="mb-4 text-3xl text-primary material-symbols-outlined dark:text-white"
            >bolt</span
          >
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">Performance First</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary-text dark:text-gray-400">
            Optimizing Core Web Vitals, code-splitting, and asset delivery to ensure instantaneous
            load times.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-border-tertiary bg-card-primary rounded-3xl border p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 md:mt-12"
        >
          <span class="mb-4 text-3xl text-primary material-symbols-outlined dark:text-white"
            >accessibility_new</span
          >
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">Inclusive Design</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary-text dark:text-gray-400">
            Strict adherence to WCAG 2.1 guidelines ensuring the web is accessible to everyone,
            everywhere.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-border-tertiary bg-card-primary rounded-3xl border p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          <span class="mb-4 text-3xl text-primary material-symbols-outlined dark:text-white"
            >grid_view</span
          >
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">Pixel Perfect</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary-text dark:text-gray-400">
            Translating Figma designs into responsive code with exact precision and fluid
            responsiveness.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="border-border-tertiary bg-card-primary rounded-3xl border p-8 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 md:mt-12"
        >
          <span class="mb-4 text-3xl text-primary material-symbols-outlined dark:text-white"
            >integration_instructions</span
          >
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-bold">Type Safety</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-secondary-text dark:text-gray-400">
            Leveraging TypeScript to build robust, scalable applications with fewer runtime errors.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
